


Link Types:

Deleting a parent does what ??

	Exclusive - Delete Children
	Normal    - If the, with the removal of this link, the child is orphaned, delete it



###############################################

Trash
-----
We should have a reserved folder "Trash" that can hold all deleted assets.
Assets in "Trash" can only be completely deleted by Root.
Assets can be moved from "Trash" to restore them
Assets can be moved to "Trash" to remove them



